caption: A solitary windmill stands tall on a lush, rolling hillside, its blades beginning to rotate gracefully against the backdrop of a serene sunset. The sky is painted with hues of orange and pink, casting a warm glow over the expansive landscape. In the distance, the silhouette of majestic mountains frames the scene, while patches of forest and open fields stretch across the horizon, creating a tranquil and picturesque setting.
